{"title":"王的象棋世界","time_limit":3000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":["矩阵","多项式 / 形式幂级数","DFT（含 NTT）及FFT"],"operation":{"submit":"https://loj.ac/problem/6738#submit_code","submissions":"https://loj.ac/submissions?problem_id=6738","statistics":"https://loj.ac/problem/6738/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://loj.ac/problem/6738/testdata","discussion":"https://loj.ac/discussion/problem/6738"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"**本题是[「CEOI2020」象棋世界](https://loj.ac/problem/3353)，其中国王情况的加强版。**\r\n\r\n一个 $R\\times C$ 的棋盘，你有 $Q$ 组询问，每次询问国王走 $R-1$ 步从 $(1,a)$ 到达 $(R,b)$ 有多少种方案。你只需要输出答案对 $998244353$ 取模的结果。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行输入三个正整数 $R, C, Q$，表示棋盘的长宽以及询问次数。\r\n\r\n接下来 $Q$ 行每行两个正整数 $a,b$，表示一组具体询问。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出 $Q$ 行每行一个整数，表示对应询问的方案数。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入\r\n\r\n```plain\r\n13 10 10\r\n10 1\r\n2 2\r\n9 1\r\n10 5\r\n8 8\r\n9 1\r\n9 3\r\n7 5\r\n5 6\r\n8 10\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出\r\n\r\n```plain\r\n328\r\n45475\r\n1142\r\n12804\r\n65715\r\n1142\r\n7995\r\n58199\r\n69552\r\n29964\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"对于 $100\\%$ 的数据，保证 $2\\le C\\le 10^5, C\\le R\\le 10^9, 1\\le Q\\le 10^5$。\r\n\r\n| 子任务编号 | $C\\le$ | $Q\\le $ | 分值 |\r\n| :--------: | :----: | :-----: | :--: |\r\n|    $1$     | $10^2$ | $10^4$  | $11$ |\r\n|    $2$     | $10^3$ | $10$  | $14$ |\r\n|    $3$     | $10^3$ | $10^5$  | $25$ |\r\n|    $4$     | $10^5$ | $10^2$  | $30$ |\r\n|    $5$     | $10^5$ | $10^5$  | $20$ |\r\n\r\n"}]}